      <h2 class="amba-block-title">What is the ADN?</h2>
      <h4 class="amba-block-description">The AMBA Development Network was established to provide high-potential Business Schools the opportunity to be part of a community that stresses continuous improvement and international networking. The network has been shaped to support Business Schools who share AMBA’s values and seek support in reaching accreditation standards.</h4>
