<section class="container-fluid amba-block-standard bg-amba-green">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-10 col-xl-9 text-center">
      <h4 class="amba-block-description">Joining the network enables Schools to leverage the strength and support of the AMBA family to aid their development and goals. The network offers tools, connections, and research which can give way to positive implementations and changes to your management education portfolio.</h4>
      <h4 class="amba-block-description">By joining the AMBA Development Network, you join a prestigious group of Business Schools dedicated to improving management education in the world. Alongside the increased international status your school receives, you will also have access to the following services:</h4>

